listing.name: Light, modern and spacious loft
listing.description:
Our comfortable apartment is located in the heart of Amsterdam. Close to Nieuwmarkt and Waterlooplein, which makes it an excellent spot to celebrate New Years Eve.

Every room is accessible.

Obviously we leave you with a phone number for urgent questions. (SENSITIVE CONTENTS HIDDEN) also proves to be helpful.

Just 3 minutes to Metro Nieuwmarkt and Metro Waterlooplein. 15 minutes walking to Amsterdam Central Station. 3 minutes walking to trams 9 and 14.
listing.house_rules: Parties can be held in all the bars, restaurants and clubs close by, so there's no need to use our apartment for it :) Smoking only on the balcony or outside.
listing.interaction: Obviously we leave you with a phone number for urgent questions. (SENSITIVE CONTENTS HIDDEN) also proves to be helpful.
listing.neighborhood_overview:
Quiet street, very close to a lot of turist hotspots such as:
Gassan Diamonds, Waterlooplein second-hand market (where you can rent MacBikes as well), Opera House, Red Light District, Museum Rembrandthouse, Old Church, Southern Church, Chinatown, the canals, Jewish Quarter, the Amsterdam Zoo, Nemo, Maritime Museum, Flowermarket, Purse Museum Hendrikje, FOAM Photography museum. 
We will leave you 2 museumcards that provide FREE entrance to ALL museums!
In this time of year, the Amsterdam Light Festival is precious for a walking or boattour.
listing.notes: This is the perfect spot to celebrate New Years Eve! Just 50 to 100 meters away, you will get the biggest fireworks of the city (nieuwmarkt and the maritime museum).
